Adviser John M. Poindexter and his wife, Linda, are greeted by supporters at 
courthouse after he was sentenced to six months in prison for his role in 
Iran-Contra scandal. United Press International; Table, IRAN-CONTRA DEFENDANTS, 
PATRICIA MITCHELL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
