LONGSHOREMEN; SHIPPING; HIRING; PACIFIC MARITIME ASSOCIATION; INTERNATIONAL 
LONGSHOREMEN'S AND WAREHOUSEMEN'S UNION; CLASS ACTION SUITS; SETTLEMENTS 
</P>
