Photo, Candy and David Arney, mother and stepfather of Brenda Berndt, at court 
hearing Monday. JOE KENNEDY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, William Burke in court. 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Southland Edition) Bail for Deputy William Burke was 
raised from $25,000 to $500,000. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
