Laguna Beach Open this month? . . . Answer: The Laguna Beach City Council won't 
permit sponsorship by alcoholic beverage producers, and the patron of the Assn. 
of Volleyball Professionals is Miller Lite beer. But other men pros and top 
players from the women's pro association will compete. . . . More about beach 
sports in Mike Reilley's column debuting today (C13). Mark I. Pinsky and Steve 
Emmons 
